Name: Sugary Dream
Desc: One can hardly get away from this comfortable cocoon made from down and foam during wintertime.

Name: Magical Cabinet
Desc: Who left the cakes on this bakery cabinet?

Name: Tea Table
Desc: A small, round table with a velvet cover and freshly prepared desserts on top.

Name: Cocoa Chair
Desc: A very solid chair. Nobody knows why it smells like chocolate though...

Name: Tree Stump
Desc: A very old tree stump. Weird mushrooms have grown on it.

Name: Afternoon Leisure
Desc: There are pots and desserts on this trolley. "Auntie Witch" may have put more goodies...

Name: Forest Path
Desc: An incomplete painting portraying a forest path. The wet paint gives a fascinating smell.

Name: Fondant Fence
Desc: This white fence wraps around well-trimmed plants, but gives a sweet scent for no reason...

Name: Sweet Fragrance
Desc: The potted flowers smell so delicious. Wait a sec...Are they really flowers?

Name: Flower Stand
Desc: The plants on this flower stand never seem to wither.

Name: White Pillar
Desc: Crafted from polished white stone, this pillar has a small pot on its top.

Name: Wall Planter
Desc: A wall-hanging planter decorated with flowers and greenery. Also gives an amazing scent.

Name: Stained Glass
Desc: Made from rainbow-colored glass, this window gives colors to any light that shines through it.

Name: Falling Star Ceiling
Desc: The ceiling full of falling stars. As if we were in space, watched over by stars at night while dawn would still rise.

Name: Sleeping Pod
Desc: The soundproof sleeping pod allows the Construct resting inside to recover quickly.

Name: Star Patterned Bed
Desc: A neat bed. The bedding is decorated with star patterns, and lying in it is like falling into the embrace of the Milky Way.

Name: Weapon Locker
Desc: A locker that stores weapons. Dusted and cleaned, all weapons inside are properly maintained.

Name: Multipurpose Tactics Table
Desc: A table of coming up with tactics. The holo-screen projects an unfinished game of chess, the players of which are unknown.

Name: Cleaning Expert
Desc: An all-purpose cleaning robot, seemingly the latest model. Who put it in the room?

Name: Astronomical Telescope
Desc: An astronomical telescope developed by the Science Council. Find the right angle and through which you can see the Earth today.

Name: Starry Wall Lamp
Desc: A wall lamp decorated with hanging stars. When wind blows into the room, the stars will twinkle with the wind.

Name: Moonlit Window
Desc: A window on the wall. Through it, you can see a brilliant starry sky, which reminds you of a great painting in the Golden Age.

Name: Tactics Wall
Desc: A wall with the Strike Hawk logo, simple and solid. A furniture piece that only belongs to Strike Hawk.

Name: Lab White Wall
Desc: A wall that mimics the texture of the wall in the lab. It seems to be carrying a blank memory.

Name: Kowloong Bed
Desc: A piece of traditional Kowloong furniture. It's an antique-style bed that is comfortable to sleep on. You can even read ancient bamboo books on it if you like.

Name: Simulated Military Sleeping Pod
Desc: A sleeping pod created by some Babylonia enthusiasts. It's overall very similar to the original one and has even received the recognition of some Forsaken members.

Name: Standard Military Sleeping Pod
Desc: A small but comfortable military sleeping pod that is commonly used among the Forsaken members. It can be moved around in the control cabin if necessary.

Name: Sofa Bed
Desc: A customized sofa with the Strike Hawk logo with a full bedding set. It can be used directly as a bed for sleep.

Name: Akdilek's Tool Cabinet
Desc: A tool cabinet with the Akdilek logo with a uniform and a set of repair tools.

Name: Drawing Desk
Desc: A desk for drawing. It has witnessed the birth of many popular Babylonia graphic visual artworks. You can only paint with your art tools on it as it does not have any electronic functions.

Name: Maintenance Station Type-X68
Desc: A maintenance station created by the Gray Raven. It is equipped with simple maintenance tools, blueprints, and lights.

Name: Maintenance Station Type-X69
Desc: A maintenance station specially prepared for the Gray Raven with a high-definition display and scanning function. It can provide real-time analysis of the operation of the machine under maintenance.

Name: Simple Cooking Bench
Desc: A cooking bench with the most basic kitchen utensils. It's okay to use but still not convenient enough.

Name: Standard Cooking Bench
Desc: A well-equipped cooking bench often seen with weird dishes on it.

Name: Advanced Cooking Bench
Desc: A fully equipped cooking bench. The food on it looks mouthwatering, but please taste it with professionals by your side.

Name: Wooden Dummy
Desc: A wooden dummy to practice martial arts. Some love to practice with it even when it's outside of the training period.

Name: Ordinary Dress
Desc: A basic, branded dress for summer. It brings out the grace of a girl with its simple design with a focus on details.

Name: Haute Couture Dress
Desc: An haute couture branded dress for fall. Its design combines boldness and modest luxury and brings out the beauty of a girl.

Name: Jellyfish Bowl
Desc: A fish bowl with jellyfish swimming among the corals in it. Who sent this lovely, pinky gift to the girl?

Name: Holographic Galaxy Model
Desc: A holographic generator that mimics the galaxy and allows you to hold the stars in your hand. You just can't move your eyes off the galactic halo it projects.

Name: Racing Moto
Desc: An old yet still fashionable-looking moto. It has been well-maintained, and some of its parts seem to have been modified.

Name: Polar Deadwood
Desc: A tree decorated with ARU lights that add some warmth to the cold, withered branches.

Name: Drinking Dispenser: Basic
Desc: A drinking dispenser with a small AI. It will move to the user in a dramatic way and serve drinks for them when needed.

Name: Drinking Dispenser: With Tray Table
Desc: An upgraded drinking dispenser. It can strike a cool pose like a game character while serving food and drinks for the user when necessary.

Name: Basic-type Video Game Machine
Desc: A basic-type video game machine that supports most video games. You can also equip it with a projector to use.

Name: Home-type Video Game Machine
Desc: A home-type video game machine with an extra large screen that can provide the user with an immersive gaming experience.

Name: STAR Drum Set
Desc: An extremely fashionable set of drums that make you want to raise the drumsticks and beat the drums the minute you sit before them.

Name: Snack Shelf
Desc: A small shelf filled with snacks of various unique flavors. You won't be able to take any more food if you finish all the snacks.

Name: Portable Phonograph
Desc: A mechanical pet in a unique style. The phonograph is now playing the grand opera that is popular in Babylonia lately.

Name: Purple Feathered Bow Rest
Desc: A simple bow rest that can be hung on the wall. It always gives off a solitary vibe.

Name: White Feathered Bow Rest
Desc: A unique bow rest that can be hung on the wall. It reminds you of some holy religious stories.

Name: Holographic Fireworks
Desc: A holographic display window that shows fireworks blooming in the night sky with loud sound effects and focus on the moment that fireworks bloom.

Name: Holographic FC Fireworks
Desc: A holographic display window that shows fireworks blooming in the night sky in great audio and visual details. You can even see ashes falling from the fireworks.

Name: Route Display Panel
Desc: A display panel that records the detailed schedule and missions of an outstanding Construct of the current month.

Name: Strike Hawk's Dispatching Display Panel
Desc: A rectangular display panel that records the assignment and progress of the tasks Strike Hawk has for the current month.

Name: Movie Poster
Desc: A slightly faded movie poster. It's hard to tell whether the colors are from the costume of the performer or someone's doodling.

Name: STAR Rock Drum Set
Desc: A super fashionable rock drum set for professionals. Mind that you could use up your energy playing it.

Name: Pigeon Cage Globe
Desc: A commonly seen statue in Star of Life that resembles a pigeon cage. It is created to commemorate a hero.

Name: Whale Song Phonograph
Desc: A mechanical pet with the appearance of a whale. Its classic yet innovative style makes people wonder what music it will play.

Name: 告解室
Desc: “不用担心……有任何烦恼的话，都请你来这里和我一起商量。”

Name: 纯白礼服
Desc: 丽芙儿时曾经憧憬过的纯白色礼服，但现在，这份属于少女的情感已经被她埋藏心底。

Name: Neon Lion
Desc: A neon light ornament that combines hologram technology and an abstraction style. It's said that its original design was inspired by an auspicious giant beast.

Name: Full of Power
Desc: A cabin removed from Nanami's prototype aircraft. It has been recycled and upgraded to a rest cabin. Have a nap in it and you will be full of power!

Name: Daily Practice
Desc: A movable storage cage filled with basketballs for practice. Each basketball is covered with sweat, the efforts spent unmistakable.

Name: Classroom Blackboard
Desc: "A blackboard with the words ""School Festival"" on it. Everything written here is proof of youth."

Name: Air Purifier
Desc: A simple air purifier. The stuffy classroom is in need of freshening.

Name: Cardboard Boxes
Desc: Cardboard boxes that are stacked together. Labeled with different categories, they better not get in the way.

Name: Spare Supplies
Desc: A tray of spare supplies for the School Festival. Always have a backup! Let's make sure the Festival runs smoothly!

Name: Bunting Banners
Desc: Small triangular flags hanging on a string, it is a DIY decoration item made by everyone. Use them to make the School Festival more lively!

Name: Classroom Chair
Desc: Move the chairs together to make a temporary bed. The School Festival is almost here! All spare time is spent on the preparation. Sleep on the chairs if you are tired!

Name: Classroom Table
Desc: Steady, durable classroom tables. Its wooden surface has recorded countless marks of youth.

Name: Wooden Floor
Desc: Beautiful wooden floor. Running or jumping wouldn't make a dent on it.

Name: Janitor's Lockers
Desc: A locker that keeps all the cleaning supplies. Labor is honorable, even if it is just cleaning.

Name: Basketball Hoop
Desc: A simple basketball hoop. You're running out of time—don't throw away your shot! Everyone has their eyes on you. The ball goes through the hoop with a "whoosh." With the sound of the whistle, the game is over.

Name: Running Track
Desc: Long, straight rubber tracks. Don't leave behind regrets—run! Give it everything you have. Run!

Name: Scoreboard
Desc: A scoreboard that marks the points. The score might be behind, but there is still a chance as long as the match hasn't ended!

Name: Snack Table
Desc: A table filled with snacks and drinks. Intensive sports have left everyone hungry, so grab some food here!

Name: Summerfest Stage
Desc: "A stage with the spirit of summer. Everyone has helped build and decorate it, so take a photo here!"

Name: Vault Sofa
Desc: A sofa in the shape of a vault. An apparatus for vaulting, it is also a good chair when you get tired.

Name: Colorful Wallpaper
Desc: Cover the white classroom walls with colorful wallpapers. Don't soil them!

Name: Water Cooler
Desc: A water cooler for when you are thirsty. Grab a cup of water instead of a soda here after doing sports.

Name: Classroom Window
Desc: Glass window that lets in sunlight. It might be a bit too bright during summer, but bathing in sunlight feels very comfortable.

Name: Milky Way Bridge
Desc: A bridge with a magpie paint on it. It's said that the bridge goes across 16.4 light years of the Milky Way... But of course the actual bridge is not longer than 16.4m.

Name: Cloud Beam
Desc: A beam with cloud totems. The clouds on the beam seem to be changing when the breeze passes through.

Name: Moondew Lantern
Desc: A floor lamp with dim light. Hope it can guide people to their true love.

Name: Magpie Window
Desc: A paper window with magpie patterns. One could hear the sound of the night breeze and the chirps of the magpies when standing close to it.

Name: Lotus Cake Stool
Desc: A lotus-Cake-shaped stool, which makes you want to have something sweet while sitting on it.

Name: Cream Cake Stool
Desc: A soft cream-Cake-slice-shaped stool, which makes you feel like sinking into it when sitting on it.

Name: Ice-cream Cake Stool
Desc: An ice-cream-Cake-slice-shaped stool, which makes you feel a bit cold when sitting on it.

Name: Green Bean Cake Stool
Desc: A green-bean-Cake-shaped stool, which puts you in a good mood when sitting on it.

Name: Five Nuts Cake Stool
Desc: A five-nuts-Cake-shaped stool, which gives you a mixed feeling when sitting on it.

Name: Cake Table
Desc: A Cake-shaped round table, which is suitable for family and friends to sit at it and enjoy the time together.

Name: Simple Medical Trolley
Desc: A simple trolley carrying medical devices, which is capable of supporting patients lives in emergencies.

Name: Common Physiotherapy Bed
Desc: The most common Star of Life physiotherapy bed equipped with a shadowless lamp and a simple analysis device, which can be used for some surgeries.

Name: Medic Sleeping Chamber
Desc: A mass-produced sleeping pod that combines comfort and functionality, which makes the user to fall asleep quickly regardless of their state of health.

Name: Cellular Structure Rings
Desc: A common ceiling ornament in Star of Life. The three linked rings remind people of the base unit of the life — the cell.

Name: Star Tower of Life
Desc: A Star of Life ornament, which shows how Star of Life headquarters is supposed to be like on Earth in the plan made in the Golden Age.

Name: Surgical Record Screen
Desc: A huge operating room screen that allows the medics to plan for surgeries and people assignment.

Name: Doctor's Office Desk
Desc: A common office desk for doctors to check case history, search information, and make diagnoses. However, there are a lot of complaints about not being able to find a pen for note-taking in the desk.

Name: Cultivation Square
Desc: A piece of floor with the Star of Life logo, a logo that has witnessed the maintenance and growth of numerous lives.

Name: Beehive Table
Desc: A set consists of a hexagonal table and a chair. Users can purchase multiple ones and put them together to be an organized secondary test bench.

Name: Indicator Screen
Desc: A holographic originally designed to direct patients. It can also be used as a simple display screen and set to a default display mode in the dormitory.

Name: Robotic Arm with Screen
Desc: A robotic arm that can move equipment and medicines around while accessing their data to avoid leaving objects behind.

Name: Beehive Stand
Desc: A ornament stand commonly seen in the hall of Star of Life, which combines a good texture and a sense of technology.

Name: Double-Deck Cart
Desc: A cart that carries medicines and potions, which is commonly seen in pharmacies.

Name: Star of Life Sofa Bed
Desc: A sofa bed commonly see in doctor's offices. It was originally designed for medics to take a nap, but they rarely have the time for it.

Name: Case History Terminal
Desc: A terminal used to store patient data including case history, allergies, etc., which can be turned on with medic ID cards.

Name: Wall of Prayers
Desc: A wall decoration occasionally seen in Star of Life. The walls in hospitals have listened to more sincere prayers than those in churches.

Name: Winged Snake Scepter
Desc: A common ornament in Star of Life. Its design was inspired by the snake scepter symbolizing resurrection and rebirth in mythology.

Name: Physiotherapy Chair
Desc: A physiotherapy chair used to diagnose and treat patients with chronic and mild diseases. There is also a more common household version.

Name: Stained Glass Window
Desc: A window made with stained glass, which was commonly seen on religious buildings but now widely used in decoration.

Name: Kuroro Bar Counter
Desc: A bar counter with various tools. Kuroro always plays bartender and shakes the shot glass behind the counter, but actually what's in it is milk.

Name: Disco Ball
Desc: Steel frames with lights and a disco ball that helps to create a perfect stage.

Name: Kuroro Sticker
Desc: Just a Kuroro wall sticker. The Kuroro on it is definitely not staring at you. Definitely not.

Name: DJ Booth
Desc: Mixing, shifting sounds, dropping sound effects... Whoever stands behind it will surely be busy, but Kuroro can handle anything!

Name: Clang-Clang Electronic Drum Set
Desc: The most common electronic drum set in discos. There is no way to create a clang-clang sound with it, but that's just how Kuroro named it.

Name: Super High Dancing Floor
Desc: An exciting dance floor device that will shine when you step on any of the color blocks in the center.

Name: Tuner Electric Guitar
Desc: It looks like an ordinary electric guitar, but its stand is actually a tuner connected to the guitar. Those who don't know how to play guitar can still satisfy themselves with it.

Name: Distortion Microphone
Desc: A microphone that can distort your voice in various ways. The fan mode is the most popular mode.

Name: Disco Sofa
Desc: A leather disco sofa. It's said that its original design has the function of massaging the user based on the volume of the sound in the environment. Unfortunately, the function is not included in the final design.

Name: Shining Stage
Desc: A stage with amazing visual effects, which can make anyone standing on it look like a superstar.

Name: Stereo Speaker
Desc: A floorstanding speaker with perfect sound quality able to project sound to every corner. Somehow it also has the music note visual effect just like the speaker in manga.

Name: Disco Stool
Desc: A disco stool. The circles on it are actually part of a trampoline.

Name: Volume Table
Desc: A table that visualizes the music volume with patterns changing with the volume!——It's said that the table is designed based on this concept.

Name: Music Wave Wall
Desc: A wall that turns music into visual art. The moving patterns make people can't help but wag their heads in time to the music.

Name: Kuroro Display Case
Desc: A display case placed in the most prominent spot. The bottles in it all have the Kuroro logo on them. Is the case too tall for the user? Well, there's no need to worry about that.

Name: Score Monster
Desc: It's a good idea to play darts in your spare time as long as you don't get mad when you score low.

Name: Throne
Desc: A single-seater leather sofa in a unique color. It goes without saying how important the person who sits on it is.

Name: Godfather's Coat Rack
Desc: A wooden coat tree that is stable, elegant, low-key, yet luxurious.

Name: Areca Palm
Desc: A lush plant with big leaves. It's said that it brings good luck to your career.

Name: Kingpin's Round Table
Desc: A round table temporarily used for work. It comes with all the office items you can imagine.

Name: Spring Scenery Window
Desc: A well-designed window with branches seeming to stick out from it.

Name: Marble Stool
Desc: A delicate stool carved out from an entire rock. It feels a bit cold to sit on it.

Name: Rockery Ornament
Desc: A stone floor ornament It looks like the miniature of a famous mountain.

Name: Stone Go Board
Desc: A bluestone table with a tea set and a go board. You can spend most of your day sitting at it.

Name: Greeting Pine
Desc: An evergreen plant ornament. Its branches seem to be greeting the guests.

Name: Mosaic Floor
Desc: When technology turns fineness into crudeness, the past has also been recorded.

Name: Green Grating
Desc: A lively grating, through which one could see the world in the deep alley.

Name: Colorful Ceiling
Desc: You will forget about your worries just by hearing the names of delicacies.

Name: Moment of Respite
Desc: A simple, spacious design for a free and comfy space.

Name: Good Sleep Rocking Chair
Desc: Move backward and forward and you will fall into a nice sleep.

Name: Vending Machine Closet
Desc: You can find everything from soda water to vital fluid in it. Just make sure you don't pick the wrong one.

Name: Square Restaurant Table
Desc: A square table with a menu between the glass and the tabletop. Its big size always makes the "standard menu" looks small on it.

Name: Round Restaurant Table
Desc: A round table with a menu between the glass and the tabletop. Its small size makes it convenient to order with the "standard menu."

Name: Restaurant Folding Chair
Desc: A simple space-saving folding chair with multiple usages.

Name: Beverage Box
Desc: These simple boxes are easy to be piled up and can be opened anywhere to serve drinks.

Name: Dining Car
Desc: An all-weather general-purpose vehicle that can be used on all kinds of occasions, especially good at missions in downtown areas. It is filled with popular delicacies.

Name: Chinese Lantern
Desc: One part of it was made by the passage of time, and the other part of it was made of iron.

Name: Plastic Stool
Desc: When piled together, these plastic stools will become stronger than expected. Combine them with wood boards to set up a table for temporary use.

Name: Traffic Light
Desc: You might be able to find delicacies following the light... Anyways, you won't walk to the outside.

Name: Red Envelope Citrus Tree
Desc: A citrus tree that carries good wishes.

Name: Firecrackers Decoration
Desc: It's a decoration that can't be ignited. However, people still believe it can chase away bad luck.

Name: Chinese Character Decoration
Desc: A lucky charm that can be stuck to a wall. Such decorations have been disappearing over time.

Name: Nostalgic Screen
Desc: A simple, unique, nostalgic screen that divides a room.

Name: Retro Screens
Desc: Not fashionable, nor ancient, they just stand there with other old items, creating a special style.

Name: Knight's Dream
Desc: Soft and comfy, it is also the portal to the dragon's life mission.

Name: Precious Collection
Desc: The books are precious, but so is the old bookshelf that passed down through generations.

Name: Smart Brain
Desc: A table with piles of research materials. A knight should be armed with more than just a sword and an armor.

Name: Symbol of Lordship
Desc: With its high back showing lordship power, the chair provides a moment of rest for its user.

Name: Weapons of Glory
Desc: A sword and a shield of glory. Perhaps this combination will release miraculous power.

Name: Nature's Embrace
Desc: Fall asleep in this carefully made tent hammock and the company of nature.

Name: Fruits and Veggies
Desc: Freshly picked fruits and veggies are placed on a cart, making it possible for them to appear on your stove no matter where it is.

Name: Minimalism
Desc: High-end minimalism usually consists of the simplest materials. For example, several ropes and some wood.

Name: Lawn Stool
Desc: A stool inspired by lawn. It looks like a piece of lawn uprooted from the ground and planted in a wooden basin.

Name: Fruit and Veggie Pool
Desc: Let the fruits and veggies wash themselves clean while swimming for the last time.

Name: Fluffy Haicma
Desc: A fluffy plush toy designed based on Haicma. Nanami insists that it should be smiling.

Name: Glorious Days
Desc: Excitement, happiness, and sadness... She let herself indulge in the emotions, walking slowly down memory lane. It ends playing. The coordinates of the future are still in the distance. She has to put them away in her heart and set off again.

Name: Tea Party Table
Desc: A carefully arranged long table. It indicates that a special tea party is about to begin.

Name: Dessert Party
Desc: A delicious aroma comes from the various baked desserts on the table.

Name: Tea Time
Desc: A comfortable armchair that will put you in an elegant and relaxing posture.

Name: Mr. Bunny
Desc: Mr. Bunny hugs the potted plant he cares for each day, creating a dreamlike atmosphere for tea parties.

Name: Wonderland Invitation
Desc: A board with "Tea Time" written on it. When does the tea party start?

Name: Fantasy World
Desc: A fence entwined with morning glory and green vines. Entering is like stepping into a dream.

Name: Truther Seeker Sofa
Desc: A soft and comfy old-fashioned sofa. Taking a nap on it may bring inspiration.

Name: Thinking Chair
Desc: A wooden chair used by detectives. It's said to help one's concentration.

Name: Unveiling Desk
Desc: An antique desk containing many small items used by a detective hidden within.

Name: Deduction Table
Desc: A round table with a chessboard. An exquisite battle of the minds is about to commence.

Name: Inspiration Fireplace
Desc: A fireplace pulsing with orange flames. Gazing into it, you may see sparks of inspiration.

Name: Detective Board
Desc: A board full of clues and pictures. A spiderweb-like trail will eventually lead to the truth.

Name: Audiophile Cabinet
Desc: A display cabinet filled with CDs. Headphones fit for true audiophiles can block out the world to enjoy music to the fullest.

Name: Ruins of the End
Desc: A scarlet katana is stuck in the rubble. What kind of battle has it survived?

Name: Sea of Books Bookshelf
Desc: A bookshelf holding a large number of books. You can find all kinds of books in it.

Name: Warm Tea
Desc: A book and a cup of tea under the light. May this time of peace last forever.

Name: Cotton Cushion Chair
Desc: The soft cushion makes you don't want to stand up once you sit on it.

Name: Trolley
Desc: A trolley used to transport items. It's full of books now.

Name: Universe Gaze
Desc: A telescope for observing the starry sky.

Name: Tea Cabinet
Desc: Good tea needs no bush. Boil a pot of good tea and enjoy a happy family time.

Name: Flowing Stream
Desc: A long table inspired by streams, full of traditional festive foods.

Name: Hollyhock Chair
Desc: A traditional low chair, whose cushion has a faint scent.

Name: Rice's Aroma Stove
Desc: A stove that burns firewood as fuel. It's said that the rice you cook with firewood yourself is especially tasty.

Name: Pouring Greenness
Desc: A green willow leaf ornament. Looks cute when blowing in the wind.

Name: Grass Ornament
Desc: An ornament made of grass. It symbolizes the virtue of human beings.

Name: Firefly Memory
Desc: The firefly that only stays here. The lonely, comfortable swing. The evergreen vines... To him, these are the memory, the present, and the future.

Name: Classic Style
Desc: A classic-style floor tile.

Name: Sunset Electric Wave
Desc: A wall with an electronic screen. The sunset pattern on it is very popular among customers.

Name: Neon Sky
Desc: A ceiling with spotlights. It seems that the color of the lights can change with the music.

Name: Locomotive Sofa
Desc: A sofa modified from a locomotive. It's surprisingly comfortable.

Name: Car Back Sofa
Desc: A sofa modified from a car back. It has a strange structure but is surprisingly stable.

Name: Car Bed
Desc: A bed modified from a chassis. You can take a nap on it when you're tired.

Name: Old Style Freezer
Desc: A freezer filled with alcohols. The bartenders' performance is the biggest selling point of the restaurant.

Name: Vendor Machine GOGO
Desc: A vender machine filled with cold drinks. You could get another drink for free if you're lucky enough.

Name: Nostalgia
Desc: A dinner table with an old BCL receiver that contains hundreds of classic radio show recordings from the Golden Age.

Name: Restaurant Chair
Desc: A simple restaurant chair, sturdy and durable.

Name: Hit Song
Desc: A music cabinet that creates atmosphere for the restaurant. It will keep playing the classic pop music of the present century during the opening hours.

Name: Four-Stroke Bar Counter
Desc: It's said that it is a bar counter modified from a real car engine, but it can't quadruple the staff's work efficiency.

Name: Dusk
Desc: Let the time stop at this moment and make the sunset eternal.

Name: This Way Please
Desc: The sign means, "This way please."

Name: Sunset Light
Desc: A light board made with numerous light bulbs. The light golden light is just like the lingering light of the setting sun.

Name: Golden Age
Desc: The frame holds a memory that one will cherish forever.

Name: Starless Night
Desc: She will guard your dream even in the darkest starless night.

Name: Magnificence
Desc: The sun rises in the sky to shine on the magnificent view below. The dews descend upon the land, reflecting glamorous colors under the sunlight.

Name: Dream of Ginkgos
Desc: A bed decorated with golden ginkgo leaves. Will their delicate fragrance appear even in a dream?

Name: Feast Under the Moon
Desc: A feast of mooncakes and hairy crabs foreshadows the next reunion under the full moon.

Name: Moon Drumstool
Desc: A drumstool with a soft bamboo mat. Comfortable to sit on, necessary for a nice, long chat.

Name: Grape Arbor
Desc: An arbor full of perfectly ripe grapes that will fill a mouth with sweet, juicy delight.

Name: Moonlit Basket
Desc: A flower basket that carries an aura of the full moon.

Name: Crystal Fantasy
Desc: No girls can resist a delicate cabinet with a set of exquisite dolls like this one.

Name: Candy Workbench
Desc: A candy-colored workbench with a full set of tools for not only doll making but also for a little girl's dream.

Name: Sewing Dreams
Desc: Those candy-colored dolls are sewn here and sent to every child's dream.

Name: Candy Workchair
Desc: A candy-colored workchair. Only by sitting on an enjoyable chair can one make the cutest doll ever.

Name: Circular Showcase
Desc: A panoramic showcase placed in a studio. Designers often put their recent design inspirations in it.

Name: Dreamy White Blossoms
Desc: The white florets in the dream are blooming in this pot, along with countless candies and lovable dolls.

Name: Design Toolboard
Desc: A toolboard that hangs various design and sewing tools. Incredibly handy for every designer.

Name: Tranquil Toy Box
Desc: A little box with a blue bow, which stores some toys, a faded photo, and Bambinata's sleeping memories.

Name: Levi-Gun Repair Bench
Desc: This repair bench was developed on Gray Raven's special request. Its delicate design matches the Luminance frame perfectly and allows Liv to conveniently adjust the parameters of her Levi-Guns.

Name: Shadow Tiles
Desc: With a simplistic design, these matte tiles are good for precision optical environments.

Name: Shadow Wall
Desc: This dark metal wall is great at absorbing light.

Name: Ceiling Lamps
Desc: A very common lamp often seen in studios, but comes with an auto light detection feature.

Name: Modern Lounge Chair
Desc: The boundary between sofa and chair is not very clear here, but it feels surprisingly comfortable to sit on it.

Name: Smart Bed
Desc: This smart device can monitor the sleeper's vital signs. The additional surveillance screen is said to have the ability to receive other signals. Perhaps it can be used to watch Babylonia's latest shows.

Name: Photo Cabinet
Desc: No photographer can resist the urge to showcase their works here.

Name: Optic Workbench
Desc: Lens of various focal lengths, reflectors, lighting kits... One can never have enough tools.

Name: Studio Counter
Desc: The photos still need a little longer to print. How about a cup of coffee for now?

Name: Post-editing Workbench
Desc: Apart from great photography skills, the post-editing process is equally important in making a good photo—especially for those who care a lot about their looks.

Name: Exposure Center
Desc: A very professional device that should only be used by professionals.

Name: Printing Center

Desc: When the world becomes noisy, have a seat and let the wind carry away your busyness, feel the silent passage of time.

Name: Faintly Lit Desk
Desc: Do you ever reminisce about those simple afternoons when you doodled on your desk?

Name: Starry Dreams
Desc: Each and every piece in this drawer is the manifestation of infinite dreams and pure wishes.

Name: Follow Your Heart
Desc: The moon carries the stars, setting sail across the sea of wishes.

Name: Cascade of Light and Shadows
Desc: An ethereal moment where light meets the shadows and dreams meet reality.

Name: Hopping Field
Desc: On this special checkers board, each chess piece dreams of victory. After all, reality is cruel and the loser becomes dinner.

Name: Fresh Stock
Desc: Modified from a giant carrot—"Don't steal the carrots from my storage! And don't eat my storage!"

Name: Spinning Vitamin
Desc: This windmill is not just an ornament, it also grinds carrot dust from itself with every spin.

Name: Nutritious Dreams
Desc: "You'll wake up energized every morning as if you've used premium fertilizers"—That sure is one flavorful ad.

Name: Carrot Cabinet
Desc: This cabinet displays lots of valuable treasures, but of course, the rabbits left the best spot for carrot seeds.

Name: "This is not a carrot"
Desc: Even with the emphasis, there are still a lot of rabbits who end up at the dentist's every day because they want to have a taste.

Name: "Mr Owl"
Desc: Dusting off forgotten items, the tiny instances of the past are still clear as day. Time passes in the blink of an eye, the hatchling is now fully fledged.

Name: Poker Crossbeam
Desc: A stone beam with hanging heart-shaped cards. As you look up, it almost feels like you are in a dream.

Name: Dream Chamber
Desc: Its steadfast walls shield the dreamer against the biting cold winds, allowing rosy dreams to slumber and bloom within.

Name: Spade Heart Tiles
Desc: Step upon the tiles etched with hearts, and find yourself in a land of fairy tales.

Name: Tender Scarlet Dream
Desc: Surrender to a drowsy embrace, and dream a dream that yearns to never end.

Name: Spade Heart Throne
Desc: A throne for the lord of dreams adorned with a splendid heart is a symbol of its ruler's grace.

Name: Dreamweaver Couch
Desc: A velvet seat reserved for the Dream Palace's guests, who shall find tranquility in its soft embrace.

Name: Fairyland Cabinet
Desc: The fairy tales of childhood may one day gather dust on tall shelves, yet some will never outgrow the wonder or stop chasing their dreams

Name: Magical Melody Desk
Desc: The banquet table of the Dream Palace, where guests gather to share a feast of fairy-tale bliss.

Name: Afternoon Tea
Desc: Exquisite desserts and aromatic tea set the stage for a blissful, carefree afternoon tea.

Name: Cloudstone Cabinet
Desc: A marble cabinet table with doors featuring delicate plum blossom carvings, blending beauty with function.

Name: Dreamy Sweetness
Desc: Chocolate-topped cake, with a thin, crisp shell coated in golden cream, melting away on the tongue in a wave of soothing sweetness.

Name: Spades Palace Guard
Desc: The sentry with rabbit ears stands vigilant, faithfully guarding the realm of dreams.

Name: Diamond Screen
Desc: A screen adorned with square diamonds, solemn and dignified, reflecting the status of its owner.

Name: Poker Divider
Desc: A card-themed divider with red and black hearts, giving the space a sense of fantasy and novelty.

Name: Sleepless Pendulum Clock
Desc: What ties reality to dreams, if not time itself, unyielding, tirelessly passing day and night?

Name: Iridescent Panel
Desc: A tapestry of hues, brushstrokes as fleeting as a dream, where each square hides the deep secrets of a dream.

Name: Iridescent Ellipse
Desc: The cards dance softly. Heart-shaped coins scatter like a galaxy of stars or the fragments of a dream.

Name: Vibrant Dreamgate
Desc: A keyhole-shaped door. Open it, and perhaps you may find yourself in a magical world of fairy tales.

Name: Dream Dormer
Desc: A stained glass window whose colors dance in the sunlight, filling the room with a shifting, dreamlike glow.

Name: Froggie Sofa
Desc: A sofa featuring Froggie, soft and comfortable to sit on and ideal for lounging or drifting off to sleep.

Name: Solitary Devourer
Desc: When you're alone, give the cabinets a wide berth. Stand where the light hits and let your shadow guide you.

Name: Hetero Injection
Desc: Only blue blood flows here. If you see red, get away from the light fast and watch out for your shadow playing tricks on you.

Name: The Declaration of Lost Paths
Desc: The sign's changed again. It now warns, "Do not look at the sign."

Name: Crimson Omen
Desc: This machine is for rest, but once you close your eyes, you'll hear the gurgle of water, smell a fishy stench, and feel the warmth of thick, hot blood.

Name: Shadowed Quiet
Desc: The chair is your sanctuary, but make sure you're shrouded in shadow when you sit and don't move a muscle.

Name: Silent Watcher
Desc: It's scrutinizing your every move. Don't meet its gaze.

Name: Orange Flame Knight
Desc: The thrill of the pedal, forever and ever.

Name: Swift Warrior
Desc: Our motto: Speed up!

Name: Iron-Armed Fighter
Desc: When you lift it, you lose the power to embrace. When you lower it, you lose the power to defend.

Name: Rhythmic Fighter
Desc: Unfortunately, violence begets violence. A gentler touch is always the wiser choice.

Name: Spine Warrior
Desc: A machine that will test your arm strength to the limit, but your true opponent is nobody but you.

Name: Fountain of Vitality
Desc: "Who among you still dares to conquer this seemingly simple dumbbell exercise?"

Name: Sixfold Drive
Desc: To train safely, you must balance the power of your six arms. Controlling that power is far more challenging than simply unleashing it.

Name: Fun Crispy Chip Sofa
Desc: The ultimate stay-at-home companion, overflowing with crispy potato chips. Dive in and let the savory aroma wash away all your worries.

Name: Luminous Star Voyage
Desc: Built with cutting-edge technology, the hull is sturdy and the power is stable, ensuring a comfortable journey through the cosmos. Sleep? Is that even a thing on the requirements list...

Name: Starforge Locker
Desc: Put something inside, it doesn't matter what. What's important is the mechanical click of the door opening and closing.

Name: Throne of the Mechanized
Desc: Legend has it that as soon as you sit in it, a vast expanse of stars will unfold before your eyes, and you can faintly hear the engine roaring.

Name: Radiant Wings
Desc: The wings are just for show; the thrusters are what actually powers the flight. But wings are more fitting for the sky, just like mechs satisfy a more romantic notion.

Name: Silent Sentinel
Desc: Mr. Greatsword wants to stay on the rack forever. He doesn't want to be needed, but that doesn't mean he likes loneliness. Come chat with him sometime.

Name: Star Chronometer
Desc: Even small, easily overlooked objects have an indispensable role, like "I'll be the head!"

Name: Cherry Dream
Desc: May you dream sweet dreams surrounded by the juicy sweetness of cherries.

Name: Fruit Chest
Desc: Ferment the sweet aroma of fruit into your clothes. No need for perfume, you'll smell great all day.

Name: Berry Seat
Desc: The cushion is as soft as a juicy fruit, but don't worry, even if you press down with all your might, it won't leak any juice.

Name: Cherry Vanity
Desc: Adorn the person in the mirror beautifully, wishing this friend a happy day.

Name: Freshberry Cabinet
Desc: No matter what's happening outside, sweet fruits always wait patiently inside—that's the power of a refrigerator!

Name: Nourishment Galore
Desc: More combo options, more flavors. Don't be stingy with the toppings. The surprises from mixing and matching are always unexpected.

Name: Heart of the Cosmos
Desc: The star core softly flickers in the stillness, as if in sync with the universe's pulse.

Name: Vines in Clouds
Desc: As birds dart and clouds drift across the sky, vines quietly coil around the warmth of summer.

Name: Occult Temple
Desc: Trespassers will be cursed for a century, but those who can impress the two vigilant guards will be granted treasures instead.

Name: Gentle Tides
Desc: A captivating song calls from afar, luring the lost to venture deeper... Enough! Don't go any further!

Name: Ship of Glory
Desc: Hoist the sails and set course for uncountable riches!

Name: Berry Thicket
Desc: The perfect hideout for a hunt... Just watch out for those berries snagging your hair!

Name: Saltfish Grill
Desc: Island locals dry their catches here, but it also serves as a symbolic warning to those who misbehave.

Name: Coconut Tree
Desc: Don't ever shake a coconut-laden tree. Someone might get hit by—Ouch!

Name: Serene Hammock
Desc: The gentle sea breeze and the soothing hum of the waves will lull you into a sweet dream.

Name: Enchanted Dining Table
Desc: A magical table stocked with endless snacks. Flawless except for those seabirds swooping in to steal your treats.

Name: Coconut Guardian
Desc: A spacious vault where the island's finest coconuts are carefully stored.

Name: Coco Crafter
Desc: A spoonful of honey, a vanilla stick, a dash of sunlight... Whoa! It's crystallizing in the sun!

Name: Moonlit Spring
Desc: This spring asks for only a berry as the price to cleanse one's impurities with its radiant waters.

Name: "Next Chapter"
Desc: "Another soul will soon arrive, ready to turn a brand-new chapter of their story after a moment of quiet contemplation."

Name: Gambler's Whispers
Desc: Sink into slumber in the hustle and bustle and whisper your restless desires.

Name: Crate of Dark Secrets
Desc: Behind each item in the shelf is a deal, an unfair exchange, and a mutual satisfaction of different desires.

Name: "The Winner"
Desc: "Regardless of who plays the game, there can only be one winner."

Name: The Magician's Hat Stand
Desc: Same stand. Different hats, different vibes. Every time it will be brand-new disguise.

Name: Dice of Fate
Desc: The dice will always stay within rules no matter how it spins. So how to break the limits? Get it out of the dice cup!

Name: Poker Riddle
Desc: The riddle engraved on it still remains unsolved. The answer is still waiting to be revealed in the shadow and light.

Name: Clear Dream
Desc: A clear dream arrives silently and indulges you in the deepest peace.

Name: Cabinet of Light
Desc: In the white cabinet, the precious items in the carefully organized sections are quietly telling the stories of the past.

Name: Sofa of Radiance
Desc: The snow-white sofa embraces every part of your body and mind softly and quietly.

Name: Flying Sparks
Desc: Warm flames jump slightly, chasing away the coldness and noises. Time seemed to have slowed down in the soft light.

Name: Pouring Radiance
Desc: Gentle light pours down slowly like stars in the night sky, lighting up every corner of the space.

Name: Flawless Mirror
Desc: You will see your true self in this clear mirror.

Name: "Party Night"
Desc: Put the outfit on, carry your stuff, and open the moon umbrella... A party is getting started in the dark night.

Name: Feather Ceiling
Desc: Above the chasm are wings of freedom that fly by.

Name: Mirage Painting Wall
Desc: Touch the wall and feel the wonderland passing by under your fingertips. Who decorates your dream?

Name: Sea of Clouds
Desc: Singing and dancing on the holy blue sea of clouds.

Name: Romantic Symphony
Desc: Everything's ready. Romance is the undying inspiration of this music.

Name: Cello Bed
Desc: Want a bedtime story? Or perhaps... a soul-soothing lullaby.

Name: Ethereal Melody
Desc: Musical notes fall gently on the staff lines, reflecting the scene depicted in the night poem.

Name: Outside Traveler
Desc: Traveler who passes by, please stop for some rest.

Name: Forest Song
Desc: The crisp flute melody comes—listen, it sounds like a brook flowing through the woods.

Name: Melodic Resonance
Desc: The most sincere regards for you in this spiritual resonance.

Name: Warm Song
Desc: Comfort your soul in the music and let the warmth spread through your body.

Name: Otherworld Melody
Desc: I see a whale swimming by in the distance, singing an otherworldly song.

Name: Sleepless Fragrance
Desc: Take a sip of tea and quietly indulge yourself in the fragrance.

Name: Dream Collector
Desc: A flourish dream in the corner. It will turn into a golden fruit when picked up once again.

Name: Whispers of Wind
Desc: The wind will bring my longing to you.

Name: Deep Slumber
Desc: The contract is sealed. Rest assured that this darkness will guard your dreams tonight.

Name: Darkwing Throne
Desc: If you want to sit on it, you will have to prove yourself worthy.

Name: Obsidian Coffin
Desc: Sealed inside this cabinet are not just books but also the unfulfilled wish of a demon.

Name: Ember Prayer
Desc: Here, fire is not just for warmth. The flames of offering also witness the binding of a contract.

Name: Blood Moon
Desc: What do you see through this window? The shadows of night, the whispers of the crimson moon, or something that watches you?

Name: Emblem of Eternal Night
Desc: Forged from black gold, this emblem is engraved with undeciphered runes that tell vows made under the shroud of darkness.

Name: Silent Cedar
Desc: Vines entangle the night, a soft bed awaits your slumber. Be careful not to sink too deeply—you may never want to wake.

Name: Coiled Chair
Desc: Its curves wind like a quiet python. Sit and feel the breath of the deep jungle.

Name: Grove Desk
Desc: Secrets buried in the forest are always shrouded in mystery. Rest assured, nothing here will be so easily uncovered.

Name: Darkwood Tray
Desc: A warm tea set rests on the ancient wood. Time slowly drifts by, and the quiet echoes of the forest linger in the air.

Name: Scaled Rack
Desc: Emerald leaves hang low, and the jars and bottles exude the soft scent of herbs.

Name: Twilight Breeze
Desc: The warm morning light and lush shadow interweave—every parting of the curtain feels like passing through day and night.

Name: Crimson Pact
Desc: The scarlet liquid gently sways, reflecting a sly smile—the oath sealed in the bottle still whispers softly in the night.

Name: Dynamic Duo
Desc: Admire and rate the performance of this well-synced duo as they catch the wooden sword with bare hands!

Name: Mystery Box
Desc: The box is filled with unknown surprises. Why not test your luck with Aya? The knife's ready—let's see what gift awaits this time.

Name: Flashy Studio
Desc: The spotlight turns on, the camera zooms in, then a flash—follow Aya's lead to capture those beautiful moments.

Name: Velvet Oath
Desc: Cover a scarlet cape on the snow cliff. It will turn the fierce daylight into icicles and dew drops on the rainbow bridge in the dream.

Name: Frosting Shelter
Desc: She rests her head on the thunder clouds. The mane tassels swing in a rhythm that resembles the echoes of the wolves' howls.

Name: Dusk Verdict
Desc: As the doomsday trumpet echoes in the shadow of Yggdrasil, the God of War on the judgment seat observes the soul of every living being.

Name: Crimson Cast Bookshelf
Desc: Craft the dragon scales into bookmarks and wood into a niche. You can find everything you need from epics to songs.

Name: Patterned Treasure Crate
Desc: The death reaper's emblem is sleeping deep in the drawer. It's okay to have a glass of honey wine before waking it up.

Name: Howling Flames
Desc: Moonlight melts the flickering flames, making it pour into the long night in which the beasts once prowled.

Name: Fiery Lair
Desc: It's true that the nametag sounds cool, but we sincerely suggest to buy the Dragon Taming Manual as well.

Name: Throne of Lava
Desc: Look! The green enchantress bird! And the firewing dragon! ...Don't let the illusions fry your brain. Sit down to cool off a bit.

Name: Crying Bone Stand
Desc: Mind that a knife stand could bite as well. Please scan the QR code to unlock it safely. Where is it? It's right where the bite mark is.

Name: Soul-Forger Platform
Desc: For this kind of eggs, you should preheat the base at 22℃-25℃ for six to eight hours twelve hours before hatching.

Name: Flame Halberd
Desc: Smart temperature control! Triple damage! With a devil orb that can be used as a night light! It's just... it's a bit hot.

Name: Quenched Shield
Desc: Forged by orc blacksmiths at the volcanic vent. The dragon roar steps inscribed on the back are a perfect cheat for hunters.

Name: Sacred Fire
Desc: A warrior's battlecry is more scary than a dragon's cry. Tie the saddle to that struggling soul. The God of War is going to build a new throne with those flesh and bones!

Name: Lightning Vanquisher
Desc: Save the struggling souls where the blade falls.

Name: Glowy Whale Bathtub
Desc: A fluorescent light bathtub that generates glowy fish to enjoy the bath with you... Don't stay in it for too long.

Name: Plastic Bed
Desc: The bed frame is molded from Kowloong certified plastic, with portability and weather resistance as its primary selling points. As for comfort... that is a separate matter.

Name: Plastic Sofa
Desc: The secret chamber under the sofa conceals a bazooka (DLC sold separately). The seat cushions are stuffed with 100% recyclable materials.

Name: The Throne?
Desc: Made from non-biodegradable materials with built-in voice that is only triggered at 4:04 PM on June 15th.

Name: Bingsutt Cabinet
Desc: Here, you will find chicken feet, spicy strips, herbal jelly, and hundreds of different spoons

Name: Plastic Workstation
Desc: A premium form of portable, lightweight home office. Easy to set up, hard to ignore.

Name: Notice Board
Desc: A rather traditional bulletin board, perfect for posting Babylonian news or all kinds of Construct gossips... Just make sure you don't get caught posting them.

Name: Bed
Desc: Would you like to save your progress so far?

Name: Throne of Esports
Desc: Sitting on it is definitely uncomfortable—but nobody will want to get off.

Name: Save Keeper
Desc: Open the door, and you will see all your save files.

Name: Gacha Machine
Desc: Gacha, gacha never changes.

Name: Vintage Arcade
Desc: Do not yank the joystick. Also, eating buns is banned.

Name: Trophy Display
Desc: Why is this empty?

Name: Sacred Thorns Ceiling
Desc: The upturned sky is your crown. No need to gaze upward—every thorn that shaped it lies behind you, now just echoes of the climb.

Name: Hanging Stars
Desc: The stars converge here not to reveal fate's whims, but to pour the Milky Way's reflection into your dreams.

Name: Land of Metamorphosis
Desc: Every patch of soil is a scale of the earth, cradling life's endless metamorphosis. And long before spring stirs, rebirth has already whispered its arrival.

Name: White Thorn Sanctuary
Desc: The light lingers in the white bramble, where, through countless dawns and restless half-dreams, she whispered to every scar.

Name: Stellar Clouds
Desc: Morning stars once nestled in these clouds, their every drifting fold cradles her forgotten dreams.

Name: Seat of Vitality
Desc: Tree rings are time made solid, yet they hold the memory of wild, unbending growth. This stillness is not their end.

Name: Withered Manuscript Desk
Desc: With this barren brush, the soil of thought is tilled. Even scattered fragments of brilliance will take root and reach for tomorrow.

Name: Spring of Rebirth
Desc: The metamorphosis of life breathes within the water's pulse.

Name: Thorned Light Railing I
Desc: The thorn-woven fence combs the sunlight, shaping every resting beam into something new.

Name: Thorned Light Railing II
Desc: The thorn-woven fence combs the sunlight, shaping every resting beam into something new.

Name: Glory Vanity
Desc: Thorns as my comb, the mirror shows my burnt husk; dawn as my adornment, the sun paints the self yet to be.

Name: Radiance of Thorns
Desc: Deep in the bramble, a sliver of daybreak hangs—each crack a footnote. Here begins the light, she says, already racing toward you.

Name: Morning Star
Desc: Every story kept here may yet rise, a new morning star from the swirling grain of time.

Name: Serpent Bearer
Desc: The serpent's path is lined with bitter herbs, where wounds dissolve into their sharpness. Every rough edge becomes life's signature.

Name: Quilt Isle Repose
Desc: In this plush haven, it feels like returning to a quiet island. Rest easy, sip tea, and savor pure comfort.

Name: Coincidental Reunion
Desc: Around the round table, chance meetings turn into warm gatherings, filling the moment with harmony and friendship.

Name: Pale Echo
Desc: Soft notes drift through in the air, leaving faint traces behind. They add quiet elegance to the hall and whisper stories of time gone by.

Name: Welcoming Door
Desc: Words on the door extend a heartfelt welcome, inviting you into the Tea Parlor to share in joyful moments together.

Name: Wordless Ribbon
Desc: Ribbons flutter lightly in the breeze, while a maid's elegant attire adds grace and charm to the hall.

Name: Lace Wall Display
Desc: Like a wall of lace adorned with treasures, it holds keepsakes of time and preserves every memory from the Tea Parlor.

Name: Sacred Eye Bench
Desc: The sacred gaze watches over the bench with solemn majesty. To sit here is to feel the honor of ruling the Sanctum of Sands.

Name: Bastet's Nap
Desc: Doze with the lazy grace of Bastet herself, indulging in perfect rest amid the dreamlike sands.

Name: Underkey Collection
Desc: Keys of the underworld open this chamber, a solemn space that guards the sanctum's treasured relics.

Name: Order Weaver
Desc: Sit here and feel the pull of law and order, as though weaving the world's balance in the Sanctum of Sands.

Name: Lion Torch Altar
Desc: Lions keep watch while torchlight burns bright. This table stands as an altar, bearing the honor and glory of the Sanctum of Sands.

Name: Soul Ferry Platform
Desc: The Soul Ferry Platform brings an air of mystery and sanctity, shaping the Sanctum of Sands with a sacred aura.

Name: Heaventhread Sewing Machine
Desc: Needle and thread move in rhythm. This sewing machine helps you craft belongings that are uniquely your own.

Name: クロロトーテムポール
Desc: 世界政府芸術協会が発掘した遺物。古代の人類はこれをある種のシンボルや祈祷に用いた

Name: クロロオペラハウス
Desc: 地球上の某所に存在する帆船や貝殻を模した歌劇場…のはずだが何か別の要素が混ざっているようだ。

Name: ビッグ·クロロ
Desc: クロロが正確な時間を教える。

Name: クロロ·イッツァ
Desc: 地球上の某古代文明の遺跡を模した置物。不思議なトーテムのホログラムが浮かび上がる。

Name: 真珠の耳飾りのセリカ
Desc: 黄金時代よりさらに昔の有名画家の作品。耳飾りをつけた少女が描かれている。

Name: セリカの微笑
Desc: 奥深く謎めいた絵画。空中庭園で最も美しい作品と言われている（WARNING：この記述は改ざんの形跡が検出されました）

Name: Unarmed Repose
Desc: Cool the forged light; still the feathered storm.

Name: Ops Planner
Desc: Strategists of glory, their spirits kindled for the fray.

Name: Horned Glory
Desc: Forged in the untamed bones of the mountain's storm, unyielding, eternal.

Name: Armored Wyrmling
Desc: As if a true dragon lies within, it pulsates with a mysterious radiance.

Name: Martial Curios
Desc: A reliquary of courage, built to cradle steel and showcase hard-won trophies.

Name: Embers Contained
Desc: Caged secrets rumble like a dragon's song, stirring the restless will within.

Name: Velvet Dusk
Desc: The deep crimson velvet pulses like a heart, whispering ancient curses and desire.

Name: Evil's Slumber
Desc: May you rest in eternal sleep, and in doing so, find peace.

Name: Unveiled Insight
Desc: It veils a hollow shell, yet sees the truth with piercing clarity.

Name: Sanguine Carapace
Desc: Through shifting silver mists, over earth of blood and ash.

Name: Gilded Shedding
Desc: Devouring the stakes, it transforms raw greed.

Name: The Hermitage
Desc: Twinkling mischievous stars follow along, full of playful mischief!

Name: Vermillion Drake
Desc: On shimmering wings, it guides you through the everlasting night.

Name: Serene Luminary
Desc: Radiance flows through the night, coloring moments of calm and easing every trace of fatigue.

Name: Absolute Velocity
Desc: Fast on the curve, legend on the track!

Name: Kuroro Thunder Gate
Desc: Designed based on a famous tourism spot on the earth, there is a huge red Kuroro lantern hanging in the middle.

Name: Kuroro Totem
Desc: It is found that humans in ancient times built such totems as serve to symbols and blessings, according to a research from the Association of Art.

Name: Kuroro Opera House
Desc: A sail-shaped theater building on the earth. But for some reason, there seems to be a Kuroro standing there.

Name: Kuroro Temple
Desc: A model based on a temple building on Earth.

Name: Kuroro Needle
Desc: A model based on a landmark building on Earth.

Name: Great Kuroro Sphinx
Desc: A golden model made according to historical and archaeological records, but its face looks a bit familiar…

Name: Big Kuroro
Desc: Ding-dong, ding-dong. Kuroro chimes for you.

Name: Kuroro City Ruins
Desc: An ornament made in accordance with an archeological site on Earth. A mysterious image will be projected on it.

Name: Celica with Pearl Earrings
Desc: The painting depicts a woman wearing a pearl earring.

Name: Mona Celica
Desc: It can be called the most beautiful painting of E-02 'Babylonia' so far. (Warning! The description data has been maliciously modified)
